  <name>Loukai</name>
  <summary>Real-time karaoke player with stem control and coaching</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Loukai is a professional karaoke player that supports multiple formats including
      KAI (stem-separated audio), CDG, and standard audio files. It features real-time
      audio mixing, vocal effects, pitch coaching, and a web interface for song requests.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Play KAI files with separated stems (vocals, drums, bass, other)</li>
      <li>CDG+MP3 support with synchronized graphics</li>
      <li>Real-time vocal effects (autotune, reverb, echo)</li>
      <li>Independent PA and IEM outputs for performers</li>
      <li>Pitch coaching and vocal analysis</li>
      <li>Web-based song request system</li>
      <li>Butterchurn visualizations and effects</li>
      <li>Queue management and playlist support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

